			<span class="cat-links"><a href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/category/cryptography/" title="View all posts in Cryptography" rel="category tag">Cryptography</a></span>
		</div>
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/2012/01/10/cours-de-cryptographie-de-luniversite-de-stanford/" rel="bookmark">Cours de cryptographie de l&#8217;université de Stanford</a></h1>
		<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="entry-date"><a href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/2012/01/10/cours-de-cryptographie-de-luniversite-de-stanford/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2012-01-10T19:21:58+00:00">January 10, 2012</time></a></span> <span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/author/cedric/" rel="author">Cédric</a></span></span>			<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/2012/01/10/cours-de-cryptographie-de-luniversite-de-stanford/#comments" title="Comment on Cours de cryptographie de l&#8217;université de Stanford">2 Comments</a></span>
