			<span class="cat-links"><a href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/category/cryptography/" title="View all posts in Cryptography" rel="category tag">Cryptography</a>, <a href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/category/internet/" title="View all posts in Internet" rel="category tag">Internet</a>, <a href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/category/security/" title="View all posts in Security" rel="category tag">Security</a>, <a href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/category/technology/" title="View all posts in Technology" rel="category tag">Technology</a></span>
